			"content_html": "<p><a href=\"http://curtclifton.net/twitter-quitter\">After some reflection, I’ve concluded that even posting to Twitter is just providing content to a platform for hate and anger. I can’t fix that problem, but I can stop contributing to the platform. And so I will.</a></p>\n",
